    <item>
      <title>Smart Polling</title>
      <link>https://buenhyden.github.io/posts/software-design-and-architecture/design-patterns-and-integration/communication-patterns/hybrid-communication/webhooks-vs-polling/polling/types/smart-polling/</link>
